<p><a name="Common_nomenclature_-_trivial_names" id="Common_nomenclature_-_trivial_names"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=IUPAC_nomenclature_of_organic_chemistry&amp;action=edit&amp;section=16" title="Edit section: Common nomenclature - trivial names">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Common nomenclature - trivial names</span></h2>
<p>Common nomenclature is an older system of naming organic compounds. Instead of using the prefixes for the carbon skeleton above, another system is used. The pattern can be seen below.</p>
